short.ar: في مهارة "Changer Jam" ، نحاول تحريك العوائق من أجل مطابقة ألوان العوائق المعبأة.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Changer Jam is a skill game where we try to move the obstacles according to the colors of the boxes and bring them to the same color.
Colored boxes are falling from above in the game by paying attention to the colors of these boxes. We move the obstacles below and get points by blowing the boxes. We continue the game by maintaining our high score goal with the points we have achieved. Color Jam has emerged as a fun skill game designed for kid's game lovers.
